{"body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"mission-statement\">\n<span id=\"mission\"></span><h1>Mission statement<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#mission-statement\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>Mission of Statement</p>\n<p>The purpose of dipy is to make it <strong>easier to do better diffusion MR imaging research</strong>. Following up with the nipy mission statement we aim to build software that is</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div><ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><strong>clearly written</strong></li>\n<li><strong>clearly explained</strong></li>\n<li><strong>a good fit for the underlying ideas</strong></li>\n<li><strong>a natural home for collaboration</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</div></blockquote>\n<p>We hope that, if we fail to do this, you will let us know and we will try and make it better.</p>\n<p>See also <a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"../introduction/#introduction\"><span class=\"std std-ref\">What is dipy?</span></a></p>\n</div>\n", "alabaster_version": "0.7.7", "display_toc": false, "title": "Mission statement", "sourcename": "mission.rst.txt", "customsidebar": null, "metatags": "", "current_page_name": "mission", "next": {"link": "../installation/", "title": "Installation"}, "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["installation", "Installation", "N", "next"], ["introduction", "What is dipy?", "P", "previous"]], "meta": {}, "parents": [{"link": "../documentation/", "title": "Documentation"}], "sidebars": null, "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Mission statement</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "prev": {"link": "../introduction/", "title": "What is dipy?"}, "page_source_suffix": ".rst"}